org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.edgelist

Class EdgeListDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.io.impl.edgelist.EdgeListDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataSource
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    VertexLabeledEdgeListDataSource

    public class EdgeListDataSource
extends Object
implements DataSource
    Data source to create a LogicalGraph from an edge list. 0 1 2 0 The example line denotes an edge between two vertices: First edge: source: with id = 0 target: with id = 1 Second edge: source: with id = 2 target: with id = 0
